STRICTLY stars Kristina Rihanoff and Robin Windsor waltzed into town this week with a new show full of Hollywood glamour.Puttin' on the Ritz, which runs until Saturday at the King's Theatre, includes a cast of awardwinning singers and dancers plus music from George Gershwin, Irving Berlin and Cole Porter. Call 0844 871 7648 or visitwww.atgtickets.com/glasgow for details.